<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">**</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">一、为何佛陀是</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF;">&quot;当代人&quot;</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">？</span><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">**</span></span>
